Injector/Bumblebee/Double Punch:



Double Punch jumped to the left, the blast sending him flying to the right a 
dozen feet, crashing to the ground.

---

Injector aimed down from his tree, firing off two stinger missiles at the top 
half of the tank that could revolve.

---

Bumblebee took out his other stinger missile launcher, jumping into the air 
from the tree, firing off two stinger missiles each from the weapons, all 
heading for the back of Firearm's tank mode.
